for my mother's illness.

39
00:02:47,100 --> 00:02:48,500
I should have stopped him.

40
00:02:49,220 --> 00:02:50,200
It's all my fault.

41
00:02:50,500 --> 00:02:51,640
It's all my fault.

42
00:02:59,600 --> 00:03:00,440
