who can only talk big.

51
00:03:13,740 --> 00:03:14,640
What a hassle.

52
00:03:15,500 --> 00:03:16,640
Thank you, Big Brother.

53
00:03:16,780 --> 00:03:17,720
Thank you, Big Sister.

54
00:03:20,300 --> 00:03:21,440
