to be cold and cruel.

57
00:03:29,620 --> 00:03:30,680
Don't pretend to know me.

58
00:03:31,860 --> 00:03:34,220
I used to think I knew you well,

59
00:03:34,220 --> 00:03:35,680
but now I realize

60
00:03:35,980 --> 00:03:36,960
I'm just

61
