122
00:06:42,940 --> 00:06:44,200
What a fuss.

123
00:06:55,820 --> 00:06:56,660
Father.

124
00:07:15,620 --> 00:07:18,100
(Water Demon Queen)

125
00:07:18,620 --> 00:07:19,640
The Water Demon is here.

126
00:07:21,860 --> 00:07:23,600
What a handsome young man.

127
00:07:24,580 --> 00:07:26,760
If it weren't for the pure yin blood,

128
00:07:27,220 --> 00:07:29,160
