131
00:07:35,820 --> 00:07:36,840
Take them out.

132
00:07:37,260 --> 00:07:38,220
Miaomiao, you leave too.

133
00:07:43,140 --> 00:07:44,440
I won't.

134
00:07:44,900 --> 00:07:46,560
I won't. I won't leave.

135
00:08:56,540 --> 00:08:58,840
What sweet blood.

136
00:10:31,620 --> 00:10:33,400
