143
00:11:13,660 --> 00:11:15,480
Cuicui, I need to save Ziqi.

144
00:11:15,620 --> 00:11:17,520
That's a Tier 7 demon.

145
00:11:17,700 --> 00:11:18,940
I've lived for over a hundred years.

146
00:11:18,940 --> 00:11:21,880
It's the first time I've seen
a Tier 7 demon besides my grandpa.

147
00:11:22,220 --> 00:11:23,860
But that demon
has gone down a dark path.

148
00:11:23,860 --> 00:11:25,780
She cultivates by feeding
on human obsessions,

149
00:11:25,780 --> 00:11:27,060
so she's making progress rapidly.

150
00:11:27,060 --> 00:11:29,400
Even the best Demon Catchers
can't subdue her.

151
00:11:39,620 --> 00:11:40,460
Come on.

152
00:11:41,940 --> 00:11:43,340
- Slow down.
- It's true.

153
00:11:43,340 --> 00:11:44,180
They're back.

154
00:11:49,200 --> 00:11:50,540
- Are they back?
- They're back.

155
00:11:50,540 --> 00:11:51,380
Hurry, hurry.

156
00:11:51,380 --> 00:11:52,840
- It's true.
- Yes.

157
00:11:59,700 --> 00:12:02,380
You actually made it out alive.

158
00:12:02,380 --> 00:12:03,240
Is he okay?

159
00:12:03,860 --> 00:12:04,700
He's fine.

160
00:12:04,820 --> 00:12:06,320
- Help me support him.
- Okay.

161
00:12:07,940 --> 00:12:08,780
Where is Guo Xiu?

162
00:12:09,380 --> 00:12:10,220
Miss,

163
00:12:10,300 --> 00:12:11,840
why do you need the celestial official?

164
00:12:12,060 --> 00:12:13,400
Just take me to find him.

165
00:12:18,580 --> 00:12:19,860
Alright, alright.

166
00:12:19,860 --> 00:12:21,000
Miss, follow me.

167
00:12:43,500 --> 00:12:44,340
Fuyi.

168
00:12:44,900 --> 00:12:45,740
Fuyi.

169
00:12:46,420 --> 00:12:47,260
You're awake.

170
00:12:50,160 --> 00:12:51,220
What are you going to do?

171
00:12:51,220 --> 00:12:52,240
I think...

172
00:12:53,420 --> 00:12:55,340
I didn't think you should
enter the valley.

173
00:12:55,340 --> 00:12:57,260
You wouldn't listen to advice
or be stopped.

174
00:12:57,260 --> 00:12:58,560
So I had no choice.

175
00:13:04,540 --> 00:13:06,260
All right, stop gesturing.

176
00:13:06,260 --> 00:13:07,100
It's useless.

177
00:13:09,140 --> 00:13:10,640
What you have just inhaled

178
00:13:10,820 --> 00:13:12,360
is ordinary

179
00:13:12,660 --> 00:13:13,580
Softening Powder.

180
00:13:13,580 --> 00:13:15,280
It can only temporarily weaken you

181
00:13:15,280 --> 00:13:16,880
and prevent you from using your powers.

182
00:13:16,960 --> 00:13:18,140
What do you want?

183
00:13:18,700 --> 00:13:20,800
Did you harm those villagers?

184
00:13:22,180 --> 00:13:23,100
Don't talk nonsense.

185
00:13:23,100 --> 00:13:25,180
You really don't understand anything,
do you?

186
00:13:25,180 --> 00:13:28,280
I'm the one who saved this town.

187
00:13:28,820 --> 00:13:29,880
What do you mean?

188
00:13:30,860 --> 00:13:31,840
Want to hear my story?

189
00:13:35,740 --> 00:13:36,580
Fine.

190
00:13:36,860 --> 00:13:38,420
It's very simple.

191
00:13:38,420 --> 00:13:39,260
Just listen.

192
00:13:46,020 --> 00:13:49,200
Twenty years ago,
I started learning magic from my master,

193
00:13:52,340 --> 00:13:55,140
but my master always scolded me
for having too many distractions.

194
00:13:55,140 --> 00:13:57,480
(Guo Xiu's Master)
He warned me never to enter the world,

195
00:13:57,480 --> 00:13:58,660
- otherwise
- Come on.

196
00:13:58,660 --> 00:13:59,700
it would bring disaster.

197
00:13:59,700 --> 00:14:01,880
Take your bets. Here we go.

198
00:14:02,220 --> 00:14:03,660
I was like you then,

199
00:14:03,660 --> 00:14:05,160
young and rebellious.

200
00:14:05,580 --> 00:14:08,240
I thought about the prosperous world
below the mountain.

201
00:14:08,380 --> 00:14:10,200
When I mastered my skills,

202
00:14:10,340 --> 00:14:12,320
it would be such a waste

203
00:14:12,400 --> 00:14:13,680
to spend my life stuck in the mountains.

204
00:14:14,220 --> 00:14:15,060
Coincidentally,

205
00:14:16,260 --> 00:14:18,180
at that time,
the Astronomical Bureau was

206
00:14:18,180 --> 00:14:20,280
recruiting Demon Catchers
from the common folk.

207
00:14:21,740 --> 00:14:22,920
I thought it wouldn't be easy

208
00:14:23,460 --> 00:14:25,560
to join the royal Astronomical Bureau.

209
00:14:26,060 --> 00:14:28,160
But I didn't know
that with enough money,

210
00:14:29,140 --> 00:14:30,580
there was no door I couldn't enter.

211
00:14:31,820 --> 00:14:33,420
(Astronomical Bureau)

212
00:14:33,780 --> 00:14:34,940
(Astronomical Bureau)
But I

213
00:14:35,020 --> 00:14:37,440
didn't have any real talent.

214
00:14:37,700 --> 00:14:38,600
- But
- Beginner.

215
00:14:38,840 --> 00:14:40,260
- I was clever.
- Sweep the floors.

216
00:14:40,260 --> 00:14:41,100
I was perceptive.

217
00:14:41,140 --> 00:14:42,760
And I was lucky.

218
00:14:43,500 --> 00:14:46,320
Before long,
I caught the attention of a noble.

219
00:14:47,200 --> 00:14:48,720
The late emperor and the current ruler

220
00:14:48,740 --> 00:14:50,440
disliked cultivators and talismans.

221
00:14:51,020 --> 00:14:53,400
It was hard for the staff
of the Astronomical Bureau to be appreciated.

222
00:14:54,100 --> 00:14:55,160
So the noble you mentioned is

223
00:14:56,620 --> 00:14:57,680
Dowager Consort Zhao.

224
00:14:58,540 --> 00:14:59,380
Clever.

225
00:15:01,380 --> 00:15:03,480
When the late emperor was alive,

226
00:15:03,660 --> 00:15:05,940
the noble was a consort.

227
00:15:05,940 --> 00:15:08,520
On the surface, she had no ties
to the Astronomical Bureau,

228
00:15:09,060 --> 00:15:10,120
but she secretly valued

229
00:15:10,380 --> 00:15:11,760
and supported

230
00:15:12,100 --> 00:15:14,420
a few trusted people.

231
00:15:14,420 --> 00:15:16,280
I was one of them.

232
00:15:17,340 --> 00:15:18,180
Not long after,

233
00:15:18,420 --> 00:15:19,640
I received a secret order.

234
00:15:19,860 --> 00:15:21,300
Only trusted confidants were qualified

235
00:15:21,300 --> 00:15:22,920
to receive such orders.

236
00:15:23,140 --> 00:15:24,220
The order stated

237
00:15:24,220 --> 00:15:27,360
that Qilin Mountain had collapsed

238
00:15:27,820 --> 00:15:29,300
a few days ago.

239
00:15:29,300 --> 00:15:31,840
It was caused
by a great demon in the mountain.

240
00:15:32,020 --> 00:15:33,820
After the demon was subdued,

241
00:15:33,820 --> 00:15:35,140
to stabilize public morale,

242
00:15:35,140 --> 00:15:37,200
the court suppressed the news.

243
00:15:37,200 --> 00:15:38,540
But with the mountain's collapse,

244
00:15:38,540 --> 00:15:41,340
(Qilin Mountain)
other dangerous demons in the mountain

245
00:15:41,340 --> 00:15:42,720
scattered and fled.

246
00:15:42,740 --> 00:15:43,700
The noble ordered

247
00:15:43,700 --> 00:15:46,780
- that all of them must be exterminated
- Stop.

248
00:15:46,780 --> 00:15:48,040
to prevent future trouble.

249
00:16:15,260 --> 00:16:16,640
To help us complete the task,

250
00:16:16,780 --> 00:16:18,680
the noble made an exception

251
00:16:19,220 --> 00:16:22,180
and mobilized the mountain talisman
from the Bureau's Ziwei Pavilion

252
00:16:22,180 --> 00:16:23,240
to aid us.

253
00:16:23,980 --> 00:16:24,960
The mountain talisman?

254
00:16:25,380 --> 00:16:27,400
The talisman
that flattens mountains and seas?

255
00:16:28,660 --> 00:16:30,480
How could you misuse
such a powerful talisman?

256
00:16:30,860 --> 00:16:31,960
Listen to me.

257
00:16:32,940 --> 00:16:34,900
Before setting off, the noble instructed

258
00:16:34,900 --> 00:16:36,680
to leave no trouble behind.

259
00:16:36,820 --> 00:16:38,200
All difficult demons must be eliminated,

260
00:16:38,200 --> 00:16:40,740
even if we had to break the mountain.

261
00:16:40,740 --> 00:16:42,860
Protect the people?
Rather be safe than sorry?

262
00:16:42,860 --> 00:16:44,640
What does that have to do
with Zhijing Town?

263
00:16:45,660 --> 00:16:47,780
Why do you have so many questions?

264
00:16:47,780 --> 00:16:49,420
It's actually quite simple.

265
00:16:49,420 --> 00:16:51,880
Ask questions
after I finish speaking, okay?

266
00:16:55,340 --> 00:16:58,400
Later, I left my fellow cultivators.

267
00:16:58,700 --> 00:17:00,780
I was after a pair of Water Demons

268
00:17:00,780 --> 00:17:03,660
and tracked them
to a valley outside of Zhijing Town.

269
00:17:03,660 --> 00:17:04,780
I thought

270
00:17:04,780 --> 00:17:06,860
I could just use the mountain talisman

271
00:17:06,860 --> 00:17:07,980
to flatten the valley

272
00:17:07,980 --> 00:17:09,240
and go back to report.

273
00:17:11,380 --> 00:17:13,420
Just as I was about to cast the spell,

274
00:17:13,420 --> 00:17:15,300
I noticed that
there was a suspended lake

275
00:17:15,540 --> 00:17:16,880
in the mountain.

276
00:17:17,340 --> 00:17:20,480
If I flattened the valley,
the lake would overflow

277
00:17:20,740 --> 00:17:23,560
and flood the small town below.

278
00:17:25,340 --> 00:17:27,440
I tried to persuade them to evacuate,

279
00:17:27,560 --> 00:17:29,700
but they didn't believe me.

280
00:17:29,700 --> 00:17:31,600
They were unwilling to leave.

281
00:17:32,020 --> 00:17:33,320
I'm from the Astronomical Bureau.

